Python Releases for Windows | Python.org  --------- Python Version 3.12 needed
https://www.python.org/downloads/windows/

Ollama - https://ollama.com

Create Environment

python -m venv env1
it will create directory env1 (it will create a enviroment in local user path)
see all directory - dir
env1\Scripts\activate.bat  - to activate environment


Libraries needed:-
pip install langchain langchain-community or python -m pip install langchain langchain-community
pip install langchain langchain-community langchain-core or python -m pip install langchain langchain-community
pip install ollama or python -m pip install ollama

For last program
pip install duckduckgo-search or python -m pip install duckduckgo-search

to exit from AI chatbot
Type :- "exit"

Always execute ------ "python filename.py"
